<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>An urgent recall has been issued for a plant-based protein powder sold in Woolworths stores across the country.</p>

<p>The Keep it Cleaner chocolate flavoured 375g protein powder has been recalled nationally due to the presence of an undeclared allergen - dairy.</p>

<p>Those with a dairy allergy or intolerance are at risk of suffering a reaction if they consume the product.</p>

<p>'Consumers who have a dairy allergy or intolerance should not consume this product,' Food Standards Australia said. </p>

<p>The product features the best before date of July 3, 2022. </p>

<p>Customers are urged to return the protein powder to the place of purchase for a full refund</p>
